CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 28, 1956, page 16, reads: "Bachelor Takes Wife - Howard Hairston and his bride, the former Madelyn Moorer Cole, are the picture of happiness as they pose for the photographer following their wedding at St. James AME Church. - Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Crowd of men and women standing, including one distant far right wearing dark polka dot short sleeve dress and light colored short gloves, gathered in aisle of St. James AME Church for Hairston Cole wedding
